<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-47"><a href="#Literary"><span class="tocnumber">6.5</span> <span class="toctext">Literary</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-48"><a href="#Major_works"><span class="tocnumber">7</span> <span class="toctext">Major works</span></a></li>
