<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ram%C3%B3n_Emeterio_Betances&amp;action=edit&amp;section=50" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>All references are in Spanish unless otherwise noted.</p>
<div class="reflist columns references-column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 30em; -webkit-column-width: 30em; column-width: 30em; list-style-type: decimal;">
